00:11:51.280 --> 00:11:52.680
between different groups of people.

338
00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:54.280
And this is the crazy part,

339
00:11:54.280 --> 00:11:57.000
even within the exact same person over time.

340
00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:58.600
So my brain is physically different today

341
00:11:58.600 --> 00:11:59.440
than it was yesterday.

342
00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:01.320
Yes, the physical neural pathways

