00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:39.680
of why both lenses are mandatory.

358
00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:41.040
Through the psychology lens,

359
00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:43.080
we evaluate threat appraisal.

360
00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:45.560
Like how is this person mentally evaluating

